Accidentally read the following article, from the perspective of business and shelf life, why this customer asked a logistics company in the bonded area to help with canning, although canning belongs to deep processing and does not belong to the business scope of bonded logistics companies, here is the following This text might explain why the client wants to do this?
I went to many milk powder manufacturers and contacted many milk powder production lines.
In fact, the raw materials of milk powder in bags and cans are exactly the same, and there is no difference.
Then you must ask: Why is the shelf life of the bag is one year, and the shelf life of the can is two years or more?
Or ask again: Why is the price difference between cans and bags so big?
In fact, from this point of view, many consumers, or mothers, think that the quality will be much better because the raw materials are different.
In fact, the raw materials are the same, but everyone thinks that the more expensive is the better.
There are also consumers who reacted after eating with this mentality and said that the taste or taste of the cans is different!
Now let me tell you about the reason why the listening device is expensive, where is it expensive?
Why do they have the same raw materials and the price difference is so big?
Because most manufacturers consider that if the price of the bag is too high, it will be difficult for consumers to accept it, which means that the profit generated by the manufacturer is very low, or there is no profit, so what does the manufacturer rely on to survive?
Therefore, they have a large increase in the pricing of cans to protect their profit margins.
Therefore, most manufacturers mainly promote cans, not bags.
And you think that so many manufacturers spend tens of millions or even hundreds of millions of advertising fees every year. Where does this cost come from?
Everyone can imagine.
Then with the development of society, the promotion cost of the market, for example: the promotion staff of the shopping mall, the display cost of the shopping mall, the gift cost of the product, the advertising cost, etc., are also increasing continuously.
Therefore, various manufacturers are constantly adding new products, and they are canned, and their prices are also rising. In fact, this is a new product with the increase in market costs.
The main purpose is to obtain higher profits. In fact, the cost of their raw materials will not exceed 3 or 4 yuan at most.
There are also some brands, in order to promote their products, by any means, linked with the doctors in the hospital, and they will assist in the promotion of the products, and they will take a profit ranging from 30 yuan to 80 yuan.
The relevant laws in China absolutely do not allow such a method of operation. In fact, this practice is deceiving consumers.
It is recommended that you buy bags of milk powder and put them in the cans on the premise of having cans at home, which can save costs, and increase the preservation and sealing of milk powder, which has no effect on children.
Also, don't think that the shelf life of cans is longer than that of bags. If the shelf life of cans is the same as that of bags after opening, it's just that the bags are not easy to store after opening, and are prone to moisture deterioration.
I just saw an article about menstruation, it's too long.
For men who don't know about it.
Most girls will suddenly experience their first period one day between the ages of 13-15 and amenorrhea around the age of 50.
Afterwards, on the premise of good health, it will be more regular once a month.
But it is not regular enough to be able to predict accurately. The tolerance of about a week or so needs to be prepared in advance.
The length of time, blood volume, and degree of dysmenorrhea vary from person to person. Some people have three days, some people have a week; Change, no pain in the past does not mean no pain for a lifetime.
The menstrual period is uncontrollable, bleeding 24 hours within a few days from the beginning to the end, and the only thing I can do is to use a sanitary napkin or tampon to suck the blood to prevent it from flowing to the clothes and chairs.
Dysmenorrhea is mainly due to the secretion of prostaglandins. Taking ibuprofen immediately when the menstrual period begins before there is time for dysmenorrhea can effectively relieve the pain of the month. It is useless to take it after the dysmenorrhea begins.
Due to uterine congestion and excessive prostaglandin release before the menstrual period, it is easy to have diarrhea.
If it is about to the cycle, inexplicable diarrhea, basically menstruation will come within two days.
It is best to replace the sanitary napkin every two or three hours, otherwise it is easy to breed bacteria and remove sleep time. The worst case is to replace it 6 times a day, 7 days a month, that is 42 pieces, if you add the pre-prepared portion, there may be 50 tablets, not one tablet every month.
(Modify it here, tampons don’t need to be changed often, it can be changed every five or six hours, up to eight hours)
Hormonal disturbance during menstruation may be more irritable, and ovulation period will also be emotionally unstable due to hormone changes in the body.
However, the official crime rate data shows that women's ability to control their emotions is still very high, and they will not make excuses for emotional problems.
It wasn't just blood that was flowing, it contained the shed lining of the uterus.
After menstruation, the endometrium is the thinnest, and then gradually thickens. It can be understood that the uterus is a house. A house is built every month (the endometrium thickens) to welcome guests. If the guests do not come, they are all removed (menstrual discharge). Months to build a new house, again and again.
Menstruation is very inconvenient. For decades, bleeding 24 hours a day, a few days a month, and abdominal pain and low back pain. Who wants to?
But people can be born because their mothers have menstrual periods. Menstruation is to prepare for the house where you will live for 10 months when you first come to this world. Everyone should thank their mothers for regular and healthy menstruation.
In the past, many things about women were suppressed, and the society brainwashed women into being dirty and shameful. Everyone thought it was like that, but times have changed.
If someone feels that menstruation is disgusting, that the preparation of the female body for life is disgusting, it should not be said in public, girls stand up, stop thinking this way, never experienced it, and will not in this life Men who have experienced and don’t know much about it, don’t be so ungrateful and don’t know what to do. How can you be so embarrassed to face your mother and want your own children with this attitude?
Finally, sisters, try tampons, it's really easy to use.
Metaphysics refers to the study of questions that cannot be answered directly through perception through rational reasoning and logic.
Metaphysics are the fundamental laws of philosophy that seek to explain the fundamental nature of existence and the world.
The Chinese translation name "metaphysics" is derived from the phrase "the metaphysical is called the Tao, and the metaphysical is called the instrument" in "Book of Changes • Xie Shang", which was translated by the Japanese Tejiro Inoue (Meiji era) from metaphysic.
The branch of metaphysics includes ontology, natural theology and its extension issues.
Ontology is "the study of which nouns represent real entities, and which nouns only represent a concept."
Metaphysical naturalism refers to the denial of the existence of God.
Its theoretical basis is that all phenomena can be explained by the concept of natural reasons, proposed by philosophers who support science and evolution.
Methodological naturalism, on the other hand, refers to a method of research that does not say a word about God.
Spiritual philosophy is the branch of philosophy that studies the nature of consciousness and its relationship to the body, especially the brain.
Dualism and monism are the two main schools of thought discussing the relationship between mind and body.
Epistemology is a branch of philosophy that explores the nature, origin and scope of knowledge.
Ethics is the discipline of systematic thinking and study of human moral life; here, morality is defined as all codes of conduct recognized by a group of people or a culture.
Mainly divided into meta-ethics (abstract study of the nature of ethical theory or criticism), normative ethics (judgment of various moral views, and give moral guidelines for right or wrong behavior.
It studies what kind of moral code people should abide by), applied ethics (the science of applying ethical theory to real life situations, including bioethics, political ethics, etc.), descriptive ethics (gathering information about how people live their lives) , summarizing from the observed patterns.
Its examination of ethics does not proceed from preconceived theories, but investigates the real choices made and observed by actual moral agents, all the moral some ethics).
The history of ethics includes Greco-Roman ethics, medieval Christian ethics.
